* AgenticNativePlatform - Static GitOps Layout And Staged Cluster Composition
** 1. Repository source of truth
*** Top-level trees
**** clusters/*
**** infrastructure/*
**** apps/*
**** values/*
**** secrets/*
**** charts/*
***** includes vendored upstream control-plane charts
*** Operator workflow
**** edits committed manifests in repo
**** commits and pushes to remote Git repository
***** GIT_REPO_URL @ GIT_BRANCH
*** Layout principle
**** committed cluster roots and shared top-level trees define the GitOps source of truth

** 2. Cluster roots
*** Committed sync roots
**** clusters/local-dev
**** clusters/github-codespace-dev
**** clusters/minipc-dev
**** clusters/hybrid-dev
**** clusters/hybrid-remote-dev
*** Per-cluster wrappers
**** infrastructure/
***** cluster-scoped wrapper around shared infrastructure and values
**** secrets/
***** cluster-scoped wrapper around topology secrets
**** apps/
***** cluster-scoped wrapper around shared application manifests
**** flux-system/flux-instance.yaml
***** committed template with url/ref/path placeholders

** 3. Flux control plane
*** Flux Operator
**** installs and manages Flux controllers
*** FluxInstance/flux
**** sync.kind = GitRepository
**** sync.path = ./clusters/<topology>-<env>
*** GitRepository/platform
**** Flux reconciles remote Git state, not local unpublished files

** 4. Staged reconciliation
*** platform-infrastructure
**** reads clusters/<topology>-<env>/infrastructure
**** composes infrastructure/
**** composes repo-local and vendored charts via HelmRelease
**** composes values/
*** platform-secrets
**** dependsOn platform-infrastructure
**** reads clusters/<topology>-<env>/secrets
**** composes secrets/<topology>/
*** platform-applications
**** dependsOn platform-secrets
**** reads clusters/<topology>-<env>/apps
**** composes apps/
**** applies mcp-governance policy and evaluation resources

** 5. OCI-ready split
*** infrastructure/
**** sources
**** controllers
**** network
**** observability
**** security
*** apps/
**** platform
**** ai-gateway
**** ai-models
**** context
**** platform/agentregistry-inventory
**** platform/mcp-governance
*** charts/
**** repo-local charts
**** vendored upstream charts
*** values/
**** non-secret only
**** future OCI artifact candidate
**** includes agentregistry inventory values ConfigMap
**** includes mcp-governance values ConfigMap
*** secrets/
**** SOPS by topology
**** separate from non-secret values

** 6. Staged integration example
*** mcp-governance
**** values/common/mcp-governance -> ConfigMap for non-secret chart values
**** apps/platform/mcp-governance/core -> HelmRelease in platform-infrastructure
**** apps/platform/mcp-governance/resources -> cluster-scoped policy objects in platform-applications
